\newlabel{fig:landscape}{{3}{8}{Service robot ecosystem. \textit {Top row}: chassis bases that expose open navigation APIs for developers to build on. \textit {Bottom row}: ready-to-use robots locked to a single industry vertical. None of the ready-to-use categories offer an open interface for adding conversational AI, custom bodies, or research-level sensor access --- hence the chassis-base approach}{figure.caption.17}{}}
