\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {9}{\ignorespaces Three-tier software architecture. The Robot Layer (iMRP500 SoC) runs ROS navigation and exposes sensor data over WebSocket. The Bridge Layer (tablet) hosts the mission engine, voice pipeline, and MQTT bridge. The Cloud Layer provides LLM orchestration, voice synthesis, and remote telemetry.}}{15}{figure.caption.32}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:swarch}{{9}{15}{Three-tier software architecture. The Robot Layer (iMRP500 SoC) runs ROS navigation and exposes sensor data over WebSocket. The Bridge Layer (tablet) hosts the mission engine, voice pipeline, and MQTT bridge. The Cloud Layer provides LLM orchestration, voice synthesis, and remote telemetry}{figure.caption.32}{}}
